{"tid":2183943,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿：急需平板電腦作學習之用的學童可聯絡戴耀廷公民黨等人","createTime":"2020-09-01T08:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T07:01:30.000Z","uid":7439,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"371c73d6c0d8cfeb4216bd82d58513a7c4005921","tid":2183943,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p843x403/118504450_3329672667094704_8346468226203845845_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=666-xew60fYAX_CHcMW&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=0b89bcab80aa7bd0ef83092cc152e52f&amp;oe=5F745AC1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp843x403%2F118504450_3329672667094704_8346468226203845845_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3D666-xew60fYAX_CHcMW%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26tp%3D6%26oh%3D0b89bcab80aa7bd0ef83092cc152e52f%26oe%3D5F745AC1&h=5698bb62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭錦滿<br />\n8月30日 10:13  &middot; <br />\n【關於「#熱血社區：#舊平板電腦轉贈計劃」，我想說的是⋯⋯】<br />\n首先感謝熱血支持者的善心，主動捐贈舊平板電腦予有需要學童。<br />\n新界西立法會議員 Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰 博士亦已作出呼籲，假如各位家中有閒置且運作良好的平板電腦，可以交到我們各區辦事處，或聯絡小弟（電話/WhatsApp：9030-2853）回收。我們會簡單維修，並確保機器運作正常後，轉贈予區內有需要的學童及家庭。<br />\n（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/396949433812753/posts/1606019546239063/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F396949433812753%2Fposts%2F1606019546239063%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=73a9b554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/396949433812753/posts/1606019546239063/</a>）<br />\n由於我們昨日才開始正式公開作出呼籲，需要花費時間於行政、物流、維修工作之上，轉贈方面亦會以我們一直服務的當區居民為先，再照顧其他地區的有需要家庭。<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">故此，小弟建議急需平板電腦給學童作學習之用的家庭，可先聯絡早在6月份就有先見之明，已徵集大量高性能新款平板電腦的 Tai Yiu Ting, 戴耀廷 或 公民黨 Civic Party 等人。</span><br />\n好人一生平安！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748cc900c9bf7398d1be341d7379590991b26bc5","tid":2183943,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p843x403/118651567_1217092118648194_5098303430335038989_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=MTxPN3t3WSoAX91L2ih&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=9e40ec8107006eddb3ef34861cbed740&amp;oe=5F756B7E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp843x403%2F118651567_1217092118648194_5098303430335038989_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DMTxPN3t3WSoAX91L2ih%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26tp%3D6%26oh%3D9e40ec8107006eddb3ef34861cbed740%26oe%3D5F756B7E&h=8e3d6751&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"963ff155a1faf3aa53bb5f3b90421962ffd7f1ea","tid":2183943,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:51:53.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿：請林瑞華儘快與小弟聯絡，幫幫有案在身冇工開的手足。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2177429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2177429</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰談產假延長：我害怕回家被妻子責問，所以我不會投反對票，妥協投棄權票。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fQfzoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fQfzoS</a><br />\n<br />\n熱血公民區議員黃兆健向警方發出呼籲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2175005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2175005</a><br />\n<br />\n寧笠不屈：法子自從室外強制戴罩令+選舉延期之後就潛水至今<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2156650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2156650</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗民政處扮防疫 逸澤王姑娘慘遭1.5米相隔<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2155227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2155227</a>"},{"pid":"50ef5ac06c30412e5c9c44337e4434de4f5af3f0","tid":2183943,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"熱血公民又贏一仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"